### Login with Email
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Refresh JWT Token
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh_token_from_login}}"
}

### Rotate Refresh Token (Get New Refresh Token)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/rotate-refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{current_refresh_token}}"
}

### Customer Registration
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Employee Registration (Admin access required)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register/employee
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "email": "jane@company.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567891",
  "address": "456 Work St, City, State",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE"
}

### Logout (Revoke Refresh Token)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh_token_to_revoke}}"
}

### Logout from All Devices
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get Active Sessions
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/active-sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Check Email Availability
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/check-email/test@example.com
